Cheetor's famous grin returned, "Hey, you can't have all the fun now." 
He was excited, to see an old face back from the Matrix. He was 
beginging to think he was the only one that made it out processing when 
a familar squeky type voice floated to his ears. His mouth dropped open 
as he turned. That was it, he had gone insane, he was imaging things, 
hearing his own crews voices. His mind was still in a whirl after what 
Shadowcaster had told them.

"Rattrap? Rhinox?! BlackArachnia?!? Is it really you guys?" His eyes 
widened. "B...Big Bot?," he whispers as if he's afraid Optimus will 
dissaper before him.

OMWOS
